---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="brain fog? how to improve mental clarity naturally"
  description="clear thinking, focus, and mental stillness."
>
  <section class="page-hero section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">mental clarity</p>
      <h1>brain fog or scattered thinking? here’s how to clear your mind</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        if your mind feels foggy, slow, or scattered, it’s usually not random — it’s a result of overstimulation and unstable energy.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        fix the system, and clarity starts to return naturally.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>what affects clarity</h2>
        <p>
          sleep, food, light, stress levels, and overstimulation all shape how clearly you think.
          most mental issues are not purely mental.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>common problems</h2>
        <p>
          constant input, short-form content, poor sleep, unstable energy, and stress overload
          make it hard for the mind to settle into deeper focus.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>core principles</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>protect attention</p>
          <p>reduce constant stimulation</p>
          <p>improve sleep and energy stability</p>
          <p>spend time in quiet environments</p>
          <p>focus on one thing at a time</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section accent-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>simple clarity practices</h2>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>limit input</h3>
        <p>
          less scrolling, less noise, less constant switching. attention improves when it is not
          constantly pulled in different directions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>single-tasking</h3>
        <p>
          do one thing fully. depth creates clarity more than speed does.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>stillness</h3>
        <p>
          time without input allows thoughts to settle instead of stacking endlessly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="quote-block">
        <p>
          clarity is not forced. it appears when noise is removed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">checklist</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">clarity</span>
        </div>
        <h2>simple clarity checklist</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>limit short-form and constant scrolling</p>
          <p>focus on one task at a time</p>
          <p>build quiet time into your day</p>
          <p>sleep and eat in stable patterns</p>
          <p>reduce unnecessary inputs</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">related</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">focus</span>
        </div>
        <h2>go deeper</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p><a href="/cant-focus">why you can’t focus</a></p>
          <p><a href="/low-motivation">restore motivation</a></p>
          <p><a href="/why-you-feel-tired-all-the-time">fix low energy first</a></p>
          <p><a href="/start-here">follow the full baseline system</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="two-panel-grid">
        <a href="/food" class="y2k-panel feature-card">
          <p class="panel-kicker">previous</p>
          <h3>food</h3>
          <p>return to nourishment, energy, and diet.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/start-here" class="y2k-panel feature-card">
          <p class="panel-kicker">next</p>
          <h3>start here</h3>
          <p>loop back to the simple foundation and core path.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>